import React, { useCallback, useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { toast, ToastContainer } from 'react-toastify'; import { register } from '../store/actions/action'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import _ from 'lodash'; export default function Registration() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const dispatch = useDispatch(); const [fName, setFName] = useState(''); const [lName, setLName] = useState(''); const [userName, setUserName] = useState(''); const [email, setEmail] = useState(''); const [password, setPassword] = useState(''); const [rePassword, setRePassword] = useState(''); const [age, setAge] = useState(''); const handleSubmit = useCallback(async (ev) => { ev.preventDefault() if (!_.isEqual(password, rePassword)) { toast.error('Password is not unique', { position: "top-right", autoClose: 8000, hideProgressBar: false, closeOnClick: true, pauseOnHover: true, draggable: true, progress: undefined, theme: "light", }); return false; } const data = await dispatch(register({ fName: fName, lName: lName, email: email, username: userName, password: password, age: age, role: "6", photoUrl: "https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/bearded-man-avatar-man-vector-portrait_9385-36.jpg" })) navigate('/account'); console.log(data); }, [fName, lName, password, userName, age, email, rePassword]) return ( <>
handleSubmit(ev)}>
